---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cloud Infrastructure & DevOps | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="Right-sized cloud infrastructure that scales without surprise bills. Monitoring, CI/CD & security hardening. Seattle-based."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden text-white">
    <img src="/images/hero-cloud.jpg" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-navy-950/90 to-navy-900/95"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 max-w-3xl">Tired of Surprise Cloud Bills and Manual Deployments?</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">Your infrastructure should be reliable, secure, and predictable — not a source of stress.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">Cloud Shouldn't Be a Mystery</h2>
      <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Cloud bills have a way of spiraling. You start with a small server and end up with a $2,000 invoice because something was left running. Meanwhile, deployments are manual, monitoring is "check the website occasionally," and your SSL certificate expired last Tuesday.</p>
        <p>You need infrastructure that just works — scales when you need it, stays secure, and doesn't give you surprise bills every month.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">Infrastructure You Can Stop Worrying About</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">☁️</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Right-Sized Cloud Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Infrastructure matched to your actual needs using Azure. No paying for capacity you don't use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🚀</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">CI/CD Pipelines</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Automatic deployment on every code push. GitHub Actions workflows for builds, tests, and scheduled tasks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📡</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Monitoring & Alerting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Automated health checks across domains, APIs, certificates, and databases. Know about problems before your customers do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔒</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Security Hardening</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">HTTPS everywhere, security headers, secret management, and professional security practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🌐</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">DNS & CDN</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Cloudflare configuration with caching, bot management, and zero-downtime domain migrations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">💰</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Cost Optimization</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">We've helped clients reduce hosting costs by $1,000+/year by moving off bloated platforms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group" open>
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need to switch cloud providers?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Not necessarily. We're experts in Azure but can work with your existing infrastructure. Sometimes optimization is more valuable than migration.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            What does monitoring look like?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Automated health checks that run 24/7. If something goes wrong, you (and we) get alerted immediately — before customers notice.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How much can I save on hosting?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">It depends on your current setup, but we've helped clients cut hosting costs by $1,000+/year by right-sizing their infrastructure.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            What about security?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Every infrastructure setup includes security hardening — HTTPS, security headers, secret management, and access controls. We follow industry best practices.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Straightforward Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-2">Most cloud projects: <span class="font-bold text-navy-950">$2,000 – $8,000</span></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">Monthly monitoring and maintenance available.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Get Your Infrastructure Under Control</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">Every project starts with a free discovery call. No commitment, no sales pitch.</p>
      <a href="/contact/?service=cloud" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg">
        Request a Discovery Call
      </a>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <a href="/services/crm/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">CRM Development →</a>
        <a href="/services/ai/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">AI Automation →</a>
        <a href="/services/web/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Development →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Services", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Cloud & DevOps", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/cloud/" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@type": "ProfessionalService",
          "name": "Cloud Infrastructure & DevOps — OpsHQ Digital",
          "url": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/cloud/",
          "description": "Right-sized cloud infrastructure with monitoring, CI/CD pipelines, and security hardening.",
          "provider": { "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Seattle", "addressRegion": "WA" },
          "priceRange": "$2,000 – $8,000"
        },
        {
          "@type": "FAQPage",
          "mainEntity": [
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do I need to switch cloud providers?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Not necessarily. We're experts in Azure but can work with your existing infrastructure. Sometimes optimization is more valuable than migration." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "What does monitoring look like?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Automated health checks that run 24/7. If something goes wrong, you (and we) get alerted immediately — before customers notice." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much can I save on hosting?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "It depends on your current setup, but we've helped clients cut hosting costs by $1,000+/year by right-sizing their infrastructure." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "What about security?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Every infrastructure setup includes security hardening — HTTPS, security headers, secret management, and access controls. We follow industry best practices." }}
          ]
        }
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
